{"tid":916203,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[連登浸信會] [陳詠謙系列] 周柏豪 - 小孩","createTime":"2018-11-25T14:13:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T09:38:21.000Z","uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e9598454b46e97a0efd7e4c2088d3fb912822a90","tid":916203,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T14:13:22.000Z","msg":"首歌係我兩年前左右同我個ex玩填詞果陣寫比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢幾日無意又搵返出黎<br />\n唔洗話好尷尬喇<br />\n突登屎忽痕放上黎比人屌下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n手，牽引著您<br />\n平凡生命裡<br />\n多得(您在我)歡笑裡<br />\n但我怎想得到，如今的現實<br />\n剩低我獨處在孤單看海<br />\n<br />\n怎，想到共您<br />\n成為了知己<br />\n家中今天只(剩)低 嘆氣<br />\n睡過的這床鋪，與這場戲<br />\n那些都變作難忘標記<br />\n<br />\n重覆的心跳回憶，您如今已離去<br />\n還想到(當我那天)偷看您時甜(蜜)心跳<br />\n重覆的一再回想，擁(護您在)懷中<br />\n不能重溫那份愛<br />\n<br />\n燃燒的心裡回憶，願從此別離去<br />\n還想到(當我那天)親(您嘴唇)甜蜜一句：<br />\n''能相識於在人海<br />\n請別放肆離開''<br />\n不能重溫那份愛 <br />\n<br />\n不如重溫這份愛<br />\n<br />\n括住果d我覺得唔太岩音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edbef2ebc4f94b3dda3804c0d3e5267941dd5d71","tid":916203,"uid":4234,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T14:15:34.000Z","msg":"咁陳詠謙好少少"},{"pid":"b2c0d0f77a1b763d01d1ab5cff78576f4833d7e4","tid":916203,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T14:16:11.000Z","msg":"兩年前你都無拖拍"},{"pid":"e60fcf454c2b99bd92710ec5e0d0d623407eaa4e","tid":916203,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"edbef2ebc4f94b3dda3804c0d3e5267941dd5d71","tid":916203,"uid":4234,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T14:15:34.000Z","msg":"咁陳詠謙好少少"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T14:18:46.000Z","msg":"駁五刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d550e71dd3afa9263